title: Volleyball: NC clinches LCL-Cardinal outright title
text:
Volleyball: NC clinches LCL-Cardinal outright title 10:39 p.m. EDT October 7, 2015 211 CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Newark Catholic 3, Licking Valley 0 
Taylor Daignault had 11 kills Wednesday as the Green Wave swept the Panthers, 26-24, 25-12, 25-13, to clinch the Licking County League-Cardinal Division outright title. 
Christine Joyce added eight kills and two blocks, Mary-Brigid Keck seven kills and two blocks and Megan Stanton 36 assists for NC (17-1, 11-0). 
Lexie Stevens-Stough had eight kills, Emily Hartshorn six kills, Jenny Cost three blocks and Kirsten Wills 23 assists for Valley (4-14, 3-8). Read or Share this story: http://ohne.ws/1RuIrS2 More Stories
